{"tid":1666382,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"個個要供樓？】陳帆：社會事件有信心在不久將來會平復","createTime":"2019-10-21T03:25:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T03:42:11.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"71ba794256341786f4b7e9f3e2dcd15493487d02","tid":1666382,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T03:25:02.000Z","msg":"運輸及房屋局局長陳帆表示：「我們在說首置都可以做到九成，但私人樓宇，其實按揭成數的管理就非常嚴格，過往由四百萬到六百萬，我們聽到很多中產人士，尤其是年輕專業人士或新婚夫婦，都做了一段時間的工作，亦很努力籌集首期，但始終首期的數額相當巨大，所以他們在置業方面都受限制。近期的示威因素在政策制定時，當然要考慮，但對政策制定不是很大考慮點，因為我們看法是當下社會不安，或最近發生的社會事件，我們有信心在不久將來會平復下來。」 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/local/5dad14cbe603838c0a355806/陳帆稱市民置業訴求強-放寬首置按保限制屬聽取民意\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Flocal%2F5dad14cbe603838c0a355806%2F%E9%99%B3%E5%B8%86%E7%A8%B1%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E7%BD%AE%E6%A5%AD%E8%A8%B4%E6%B1%82%E5%BC%B7-%E6%94%BE%E5%AF%AC%E9%A6%96%E7%BD%AE%E6%8C%89%E4%BF%9D%E9%99%90%E5%88%B6%E5%B1%AC%E8%81%BD%E5%8F%96%E6%B0%91%E6%84%8F&d=IZFSAkWTwbXSesVVmoeERWg5BW3O7pEdz%2F%2BecHjXtrw%3D&h=57690172\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/local/5dad14cbe603838c0a355806/陳帆稱市民置業訴求強-放寬首置按保限制屬聽取民意</a>"},{"pid":"c1c23ce52af7dffa8a51ae2e4111b11aa9711287","tid":1666382,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T03:25:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6adef2dc1405ab283634041f32ef77e81ac9f457","tid":1666382,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T03:25:17.000Z","msg":"不如全港黨鐵靜坐聲討721啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1665580\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1665580</